---

<Layout
	title="AI-Powered Websites Built on the Fastest Stack in 2026 | Spirit Media"
	description="Sub-2-second load times. 95+ Google scores. AI-ready infrastructure. Spirit Media builds websites on the stack Google rewards — and visitors actually use."
	ogImage="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/pmowd8uo/production/83b595b916eeb64126e303f3fc71027c55aa6dbb-4000x2588.png?w=1200&h=630&fit=crop&fm=jpg&q=85"
>
	<Fragment slot="head">
		<meta name="keywords" content="AI-powered websites, AI-ready websites, AI-empowered websites, fastest websites 2026, best SEO websites, Astro website design, fast loading website builder, Core Web Vitals, AI search ready, llms.txt, website design for churches, websites for nonprofits, websites for insurance agencies, websites for CPAs, websites for artists, websites for authors" />
		<meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(serviceSchema)} />
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(breadcrumbSchema)} />
	</Fragment>

	<main id="main-content">

		<!-- ───────────────────────── HERO — dark section ───────────────────────── -->
		<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-ink-soft px-6 py-16 lg:py-24 lg:px-8">
			<!-- subtle radial accent -->
			<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top right, rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.35), transparent 60%);"></div>
			<div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 items-center">
					<div class="hero-stagger lg:col-span-3">
						<p class="eyebrow eyebrow-red mb-4">Websites</p>
						<h1 class="type-hero text-stone-100" style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5.5vw, 4.5rem);">
							AI-Powered Websites Built on the <span class="text-red-soft">Fastest Stack</span> in 2026
						</h1>
						<p class="mt-6 font-serif italic text-red-soft max-w-2xl" style="font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.4;">
							When your message deserves a mountaintop instead of a cave.
						</p>
						<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
							<button type="button" data-open-proposal class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-red px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-white transition-all hover:bg-red-deep cursor-pointer">
								Get Your Free Website Proposal →
							</button>
							<a href="/kevin/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border-2 border-stone-300 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-stone-100 transition-all hover:bg-stone-100 hover:text-ink-soft">
								Schedule FREE Consultation
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Video placeholder card (swap to YouTube iframe once rendered) -->
					<div class="lg:col-span-2" id="story" data-animate="zoom-in">
						<div class="relative aspect-video rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-stone-700 bg-ink shadow-2xl">
							<div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-6">
								<div class="flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red mb-3 shadow-lg">
									<svg class="h-7 w-7 text-white ml-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
								</div>
								<p class="text-stone-100 font-serif text-lg font-bold">90-Second Story</p>
								<p class="text-stone-400 text-sm mt-1">Launching soon</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Trust bar -->
				<div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-stone-700 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-6 text-center">
					<div><p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-stone-100">75+</p><p class="text-stone-400 text-sm mt-1">websites built</p></div>
					<div><p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-stone-100">15</p><p class="text-stone-400 text-sm mt-1">on the AI-powered stack</p></div>
					<div><p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-stone-100">98/100</p><p class="text-stone-400 text-sm mt-1">avg. mobile score</p></div>
					<div><p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-stone-100">5/5</p><p class="text-stone-400 text-sm mt-1">security headers</p></div>
					<div><p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-stone-100">195</p><p class="text-stone-400 text-sm mt-1">nations reached</p></div>
				</div>
